customer.description: Here you can add any news, FAQ, info .

donationText.moreInformation:
For questions concerning these events, please email 

Where do donations go?
100% of donations go to scholarships for current members.

How long will it take to recieve a receipt for the donation?
A printable receipt is sent via email and saved to your Wavelength account within minutes of the successful transaction.

If you did not receive a receipt for a financial gift you've made, please contact Donor Services by calling 1-800-555 5555.
donationText.otherWaysToGive:
If you would prefer to send a check, please make it out to "Wavelength" and send it to:


https://www.youtube.com/
donationText.primary: Please RSVP for All Class Reunion (Sept 24) -------------- $20 per person RSVP Distinguished Alumni Dinner (Sept 23) ---------- $100 per person In giving reason, please select "designate for" include name(s) and graduating class (if applicable)
donationText.thankYou:
Thank you for your support!!!

Please email email  with questions
